{"name":"Mathlib.Util.LibraryNote","instances":[],"imports":["Init","Lean"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Util/LibraryNote.lean#L34-L45","name":"Mathlib.Util.LibraryNote.commandLibrary_note___","docLink":"./Mathlib/Util/LibraryNote.html#Mathlib.Util.LibraryNote.commandLibrary_note___","doc":"```\n/-- ... some explanation ... -/\nlibrary_note \"some tag\"\n```\ncreates a new \"library note\", which can then be cross-referenced using\n```\n-- See note [some tag]\n```\nin doc-comments.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Util/LibraryNote.lean#L29-L31","name":"Mathlib.Util.LibraryNote.getDocCommentContent","docLink":"./Mathlib/Util/LibraryNote.html#Mathlib.Util.LibraryNote.getDocCommentContent","doc":"Extract the doc-comment from a `Syntax`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Util/LibraryNote.lean#L19-L20","name":"Mathlib.Util.LibraryNote.libraryNoteExt","docLink":"./Mathlib/Util/LibraryNote.html#Mathlib.Util.LibraryNote.libraryNoteExt","doc":"Environment extension supporting `library_note`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Util/LibraryNote.lean#L17-L17","name":"Mathlib.Util.LibraryNote.LibraryNoteEntry","docLink":"./Mathlib/Util/LibraryNote.html#Mathlib.Util.LibraryNote.LibraryNoteEntry","doc":"A library note consists of a (short) tag and a (long) note. "}]}